Recently sold: $379,000. Custom designed ranch home with finished walk out basement, with a deep 2 car garage.  Open great room design featuring a stunning central fireplace, custom handcrafted woodwork, vaulted ceilings and a three-season porch with a hot-tub.  Designed around the kitchen, this home features a center island cooking surface that is perfect for family gatherings and entertaining.  
The lower level is completely finished, features three bedrooms along with a family room that has walk out access to the patio and backyard.  Mechanical features include a recently updated furnace, whole house tankless water heater and stainless steel kitchen appliances.  
The yard features a wildflower garden, vegetable garden, garden shed/playhouse, fire pit and plenty of room for a pool or a game of volleyball!
Outbuildings include a loafing shed (on skids) and a 30 x 60 pole barn, featuring 14' sidewalls that includes a hayloft, 2 box stalls, a foaling stall, tack room, chicken coop, cement floor aisle and tack room. on one half. The other half of the barn features a cement floor and is partitioned off to store all of the toys. The barn has both electricity and running water, this is a turnkey hobby farm operation with plenty of extras not pictured or mentioned.  

Buyers agent commission available.
